(1) The Commission shall consist of the following part-time members: (a) a Judge nominated by the Judiciary; (b) a representative of any School of Law in a public university; (c) a representative of the Institute of African Studies at the University of Zambia; (d) the Chief Parliamentary Draftsman; (e) a representative of the Law Association of Zambia; (f) the Director of the Institute of Advanced Legal Education; and (g) not more than four other persons appointed;
